snippet.title: Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
We are happy to announce that the Surviving The Humans demo is now on Steam and Itch.io.

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1652460/Surviving_The_Humans/
https://surprisedmonkeystudio.itch.io/surviving-the-humans

We hope you can play it and give us feedback. Thanks
